criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient has recently (min. 2 weeks - max. 14 weeks) been implanted with an SJM ICD
             with the Patient Notifier™ feature;

          -  Patient is willing and able to independently comprehend and complete the study-related
             questionnaires;

          -  Patient has signed the study specific informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  have already had a Patient Notifier™ alert since implant;

          -  had a prior device implant (PM or ICD);

          -  have not been discharged from the hospital since device implant;

          -  have evidence of psychosis, dementia or cognitive impairment as documented in the
             patients' hospital records;

          -  cannot commit to the follow-up schedule;

          -  have a life expectancy of less than 1 year;

          -  are on a waiting list for a heart transplant;

          -  are less than 18 years old;

          -  are pregnant;
